      <title>EchoStar 的 Hughes 债权人聘请律师调查租赁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/creditors-to-echostar-s-hughes-hire-lawyers-to-probe-lease-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，休斯卫星系统公司 (Hughes Satellite Systems Corp.) 的一些债权人聘请了 Glenn Agre Bergman &amp; Fuentes 律师事务所来审查一项昂贵的租赁安排，他们称这项安排将现金从该部门转移到其母公司 EchoStar。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/creditors-to-echostar-s-hughes-hire-lawyers-to-probe-lease-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>具有 100% 胜率信号的交易指标立即出售多头债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/trading-indicator-with-a-100-win-rate-says-sell-long-bonds-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年有着完美交易记录的技术交易策略正在发出信号，表明在上周上涨之后，现在是出售长期国债的时候了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/trading-indicator-with-a-100-win-rate-says-sell-long-bonds-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Antares 将为第三支高级贷款基金筹集约 60 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/antares-to-raise-around-6-billion-for-third-senior-loan-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管私人信贷融资有所降温，Antares Capital 仍希望为其第三支优先贷款基金筹集高达 60 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/antares-to-raise-around-6-billion-for-third-senior-loan-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:23:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称阿根廷将把实际利率调至正值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/argentina-to-move-real-rates-to-positive-territory-imf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织周一表示，阿根廷将把实际利率调至正值，并放松货币管制，因为这个危机频发的国家正寻求继续减缓价格上涨并保护其外汇储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/argentina-to-move-real-rates-to-positive-territory-imf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁矿业公司 Volcan 计划进一步出售 2 亿美元资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/peru-miner-volcan-ceo-eyes-200-million-in-further-asset-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁锌矿商 Volcan Cia Minera 最近被阿根廷集团 Integra Capital 收购，该公司表示，正在推进出售非核心资产的计划，同时正在与债权人谈判，为未来几年到期的大量债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/peru-miner-volcan-ceo-eyes-200-million-in-further-asset-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数有望创 2024 年第 30 个历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-as-global-sentiment-sours-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国国债收益率上升，但几家大型科技股仍上涨，股市迈向历史新高，交易员们为零售销售数据和美联储讲话做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-as-global-sentiment-sours-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 22:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
